Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:24.32,落第骑士,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs29\be20}字幕  时雨初空字幕组        手抄&时轴  西行寺幽幽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.37,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k383}目标遥指最高处  A brave new word
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:32.23,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k386}以那热情的剑锋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:38.99,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k676}刻印在这片舞台的是  It's my soul(Yeah)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.74,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k393}不容任何人触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:47.72,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k398}你我共鸣的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:53.80,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k608}命运想必正是在此刻决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:58.81,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k342}尽管嘲笑我的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.75,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k394}尽管去骄傲自满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:06.17,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k342}迷茫踏在脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.16,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k299}Let's go ahead!～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:13.83,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k380}所以正是现在将其破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.73,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k390}是啊 把那堵塞我明天的沉重大门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.43,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k470}尽全力使出浑身解数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.51,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k308}以经历千锤百炼的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k374}凝聚一击 将其突破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:33.17,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k392}是啊 把那阻挡我未来的厚重大门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:38.08,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k491}起死回生的瞬间已经到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.02,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k194}绝境之高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:45.12,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k510}It's time to take a top
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:14.45,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k700}徘徊于恶魔之路  并活着走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:16.89,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k244}这邂逅是命数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:22.95,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k606}觉醒之地便是真实的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.35,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k329}在比神话更久远的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:40.80,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k309}我是火焰之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:47.57,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k674}离开王的肩膀  飞向赤红的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:51.56,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k314}何等漫长的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.81,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k292}记忆中与沙石共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:57.92,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k287}此刻扑向你的怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:01.79,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k366}即使终于平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:06.94,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k505}依然要把双翼化作长剑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:14.65,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k676}就让爱穿越战场堕落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:19.21,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k417}身穿绯红的荆棘之战铠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:22.96,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k375}若这具肉体要化作死花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:31.66,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k870}我愿意在你的剑下华丽的绽放
